{"tid":858044,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 表妹喊到收唔到聲..","createTime":"2018-10-11T13:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T14:18:20.000Z","uid":210524,"like":4,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2312465aeb0100049207646922bfd989dc510e","tid":858044,"uid":210524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:43:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n表妹今年中六<br />\n今日派dse mock卷<br />\n琴晚佢已經無笑過，即係佢自己好唔開心<br />\n點知佢今日收到成績表打黎講左句<br />\n無可能架，但我宜家真係好開心囉<br />\n一開cert中文有4 ，跟著有5個3<br />\n我真係開心到尖叫呀...呀呀呀<br />\n我見佢咁撚嘈就收左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩收到佢學校打電話黎，話表妹尖叫完就匿埋係一邊喊，到宜家仲未喊完，問我地點處理，需唔需要報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5368bf1e989545b65911f7d04188438fd5038e","tid":858044,"uid":192491,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"入含大 你同佢就可以放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f8cecb2f68adc1e1ae50e3624267556bb2bc5c","tid":858044,"uid":152520,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:46:00.000Z","msg":"呢條女真係走得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前個個都笑佢<br />\n宜家先知原來佢同核工只係爭1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56faeb89079ea7c3a19cfa8ee4cff17bdeed842b","tid":858044,"uid":141376,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思真心問<br />\n<br />\n係唔係潮文？"},{"pid":"3bb2219f5ab17eab9fe7c1d31897d7173274d845","tid":858044,"uid":210524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56faeb89079ea7c3a19cfa8ee4cff17bdeed842b","tid":858044,"uid":141376,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思真心問<br />\n<br />\n係唔係潮文？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:47:32.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7349c4858